.name
Banner
.author
Tobias Ferber 
.version
1.4
.description
A tiny utility to create surprise, surprise banners.  By default BANNER
uses an internal font that is ideal for title pages or sources headers.
You may also render your banner from any amiga font with (nearly) unlimited
font size and variable aspect.  
